Package it.polimi.ingsw.view.clientSide.viewCore.data

Class ViewObject

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.view.clientSide.viewCore.data.ViewObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClientAddressable, Addressable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ViewBoard, ViewCard, ViewCell, ViewNickname, ViewPlayer, ViewWorker
public abstract class ViewObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements ClientAddressable
Interface for all the data representations available to the View side. It implements ClientAddressable and so each object is identified by a unique string containing both information about the class and thee instance.
Author:
giorgio
See Also:
ClientAddressable
